ygData.messageBody:
From our ex-guild QHD:

August 24, 1999 - sorry for the delay, i've been really busy lately with
school starting and losing alot of my valuable Everquest time, members page
updated..not much else to do =) Another thing I would like to address is
that this guild may be in it's final days...many have left to start their
own guilds in groups which is fine but from the start we recruited way too
many people (like 80 at one point) and lost track and control over things.
I don't know for sure yet but /guilddelete may be used sometime soon =(
It's not that I no longer like this guild or anything but I have a limited
amount of time with school starting, etc. So email your thoughts if you
wish.
